00:23:28,453 --> 00:23:47,453
♪

414
00:23:51,653 --> 00:23:54,786
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Ice cream, donuts, cream</i>
<i>puffs...</i>

415
00:23:54,820 --> 00:23:56,520
<i>(Chibi‐Usa)</i>
<i>I love eating snacks...!</i>

416
00:23:56,586 --> 00:23:58,486
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>But brushing my teeth is a pain.</i>

417
00:23:58,520 --> 00:23:59,786
<i>(Chibi‐Usa)</i>
<i>Are you brushing every day?</i>

418
00:23:59,786 --> 00:24:01,786
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Huh? Yeah, but I forget</i>
<i>once in a while. [laugh]</i>

419
00:24:01,886 --> 00:24:08,460
<i>(Chibi‐Usa)</i>
<i>Usagi, I don't think I need to</i>
<i>ask, but do you brush your teeth</i>
<i>before kissing Mamo?</i>

420
00:24:08,493 --> 00:24:10,293
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Oh, well, I... Um...</i>

421
00:24:10,360 --> 00:24:14,626
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Next time on Sailor Moon SuperS:</i>
<i>"Dentist of Horrors?</i>
<i>Palla‐Palla's House."</i>

422
00:24:14,660 --> 00:24:16,993
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>The moonlight is a</i>
<i>messenger of love.</i>

